This issue tracker is for issues with the Bitcoin Core project website at
[aixcoincore.org](https://aixcoincore.org).

[aixcoin.org](https://aixcoin.org) is not connected with or maintained by the
Bitcoin Core project contributors. Issues with that website should be reported
at [the aixcoin.org
repository](https://github.com/aixcoin-dot-org/aixcoin.org/issues).

General aixcoin questions and/or support requests are best directed to the
Bitcoin StackExchange at https://aixcoin.stackexchange.com.
